I tried to forget you. I really did.
我也想忘记你，真的

402
00:24:28,530 --> 00:24:33,230
After our last lunch, I spent six months in Africa trying to forget.
我们去年吃完饭 我跑去非洲6个月想忘记你

404
00:24:33,630 --> 00:24:36,900
-What did you do there? -Work with blind kids.
你去非洲做什么？ 帮助盲童

405
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:39,590
What are you doing to me?
你折磨我嘛

406
00:24:40,110 --> 00:24:41,630
Look,I...

407
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:45,100
I'm sorry, but this is not gonna happen.
很抱歉，我们之间是不可能的

408
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:49,210
That's fine. I'll walk away. I'll never bother you again.
好，我会离开 再也不会来烦你

409
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:53,820
Only if you say Chandler's willing to give you everything I am.
但前提是 钱德也愿意给你这一切

410
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:56,420
Well,he is. I mean...
他愿意

411
00:24:56,660 --> 00:25:00,150
marriage is all he talks about. My goodness!
没错，他成天把婚姻挂在嘴边

412
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:03,190
In fact, I'm the one making him wait.
事实上是我在让他等

413
00:25:03,460 --> 00:25:05,190
You are? Why?
是吗？ 对

414
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,800
Why?
为什么？

415
00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:09,740
Because of the government.
因为政府的阴谋

416
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:16,170
Isn't it incredible?
很棒吧？ 

417
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:19,400
Monica and Chandler are getting married.
摩妮卡和钱德要结婚了

418
00:25:19,610 --> 00:25:22,610
I know. They'll be so happy together.
就是啊，他们会很幸福

419
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:25,780
How often do two best friends fall in love?
两个最要好的朋友坠入爱河 这种机率有多大？

420
00:25:25,990 --> 00:25:28,050
-Not that often. -No.
并不太大 没错

421
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:33,190
-I'm so happy for them. -Me too. So happy for them.
我好替他们开心 我也是，好开心

423
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:36,280
I'm so happy and not at all jealous.
我很高兴，毫无嫉妒之心

424
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:40,560
Oh,no! God, definitely not jealous.
没错，当然没有

425
00:25:45,310 --> 00:25:49,500
I'm probably 98% happy and maybe 2% jealous.
我可能是98%开心 2%嫉妒

426
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:52,970
-I mean,what's 2%? That's nothing. -Totally.
2%等于没有 没错

427
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:58,120
-I'm like 90/10. -Yeah. Me too.
我是九比一 我也是

428
00:26:05,490 --> 00:26:07,620
Have you guys seen Chandler?
你们有见到钱德吗？

429
00:26:10,460 --> 00:26:13,360
No. But you know who was looking for you?
没有，但你知道谁来找过你？

430
00:26:13,570 --> 00:26:15,190
Tennille.
坦妮尔 （“船长与坦妮尔”为乐团）

431
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:28,340
The marriage stuff you were saying yesterday? You don't believe that.
你昨天说的那些话 应该不是真心话吧？

432
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:33,850
Sure,I do. In fact,I think the concept of marriage is unnatural.
当然是 事实上我觉得婚姻本身 就很不近人情

434
00:26:34,050 --> 00:26:38,120
Look at pigs. Let's take a second here and look at pigs.
你看猪嘛，我们来看一下猪

435
00:26:38,330 --> 00:26:40,120
Pigs don't mate for life.
猪不会有固定配偶

436
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:43,960
A pig can have 100 sexual partners in a lifetime.
猪的一生可以有一百个性伴侣

437
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:48,330
That's an ordinary pig, not even a pig that's good at sports.
那还只是普通的猪 而不是擅长运动的猪

438
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:53,670
Yeah, but that's pigs, not people.
对，但那是猪不是人

439
00:26:53,870 --> 00:26:58,440
If marriage worked,I'd be for it. Do you know the divorce rate?
如果结婚行得通，我绝对支持 但是你知道美国的离婚率吗？

440
00:26:58,650 --> 00:27:00,170
Ninety-seven percent!
97%

441
00:27:01,650 --> 00:27:02,840
Wait a minute.
等一下

442
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:07,680
Are you telling me you may never want to get married?
你是说你可能永远都不想结婚

443
00:27:07,890 --> 00:27:11,380
-Who's to say? -You! You are to say!
谁晓得？ 你啊，你晓得

444
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:14,220
Never say never, but, probably...
话不能说死，不过应该是…

445
00:27:14,430 --> 00:27:15,720
yeah, never.
永远不会

446
00:27:16,860 --> 00:27:21,060
Oh,my God. Then what are we even doing? What is this?
天哪，那我们在干什么？ 现在算什么？

447
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:24,700
Whoa,whoa,whoa! What is all this pressure?
干嘛对我施压？

448
00:27:25,170 --> 00:27:27,070
Is this some new strategy?
这是某种新策略吗？

449
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:31,470
Why don't you put down your copy of The Rules, huh, mantrap?
你别再搞尔虞我诈那一套了

450
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:34,500
You know what? I gotta go.
你知道吗？我要走了

451
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:39,270
It's okay. I got a plan.
放心，我自有打算

452
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:47,590
-We're gonna find love. -Definitely.
我们会找到真爱的 一定会的

453
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:51,760
Yeah,I'm pretty confident about that.
我对这点有信心

454
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:56,790
That's what makes it so easy to be 80% happy for Monica and Chandler.
所以我可以有八成 替摩妮卡和钱德高兴

455
00:27:57,700 --> 00:28:00,730
-A guarantee would be nice. -What do you mean?
不过要是有保障就好了 什么意思？

456
00:28:00,910 --> 00:28:03,400
Some friends make a deal.
有些人不是会跟朋友约定

458
00:28:03,610 --> 00:28:08,140
Like if neither of them are married by 40, they marry each other.
要是两个人到了40都没结婚 他们就要结婚

459
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:10,040
-A backup? -Exactly.
你是指备胎？ 没错

460
00:28:10,250 --> 00:28:11,980
Yeah, I've got that.
我已经找好了

461
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:14,950
You do?
你找好了？

462
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,450
-Who? -Joey.
是谁？ 乔伊

463
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:21,460
-Joey? Are you serious? -I locked him in years ago.
乔伊？真的还假的？ 我好几年前就锁定他了

465
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:29,730
Wait. So if neither of you are married by 40, you'll marry Joey?
所以要是你们40岁还没结婚 你就要嫁给乔伊

466
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:31,870
Yep. We shook on it.
对，我们握手为定

468
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:36,330
But believe me, that is not how he wanted to seal the deal.
不过他可不想就此打住

469
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:39,040
Oh, seriously?
是吗？

470
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:41,540
I think his exact words were..
对，他说的是…

471
00:28:44,250 --> 00:28:45,240
Charming.
真迷人

472
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:48,090
He's just a backup.
只是个备胎

473
00:28:56,330 --> 00:29:00,030
-Hey,Monica. -Have you seen Rachel? Or a mirror?
-摩妮卡 -你有见到瑞秋吗？或是镜子？

475
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:05,340
-It's for my boat. Pretty cool,huh? -Yeah,it's great.
-这是我的船长装，酷吧？ -很酷

476
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:08,060
What's wrong? Talk to the captain.
怎么了？告诉船长

478
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:13,480
Just realizing I'm in a dead-end relationship.
我又发现这段感情是死路一条

479
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:17,580
-Chandler being difficult? -I don't want marriage tomorrow.
钱德欺负你是吧？ 我又不是明天就要结婚

481
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:22,240
But I wanna know we're going somewhere, that I'm not wasting time.
我只是想知道 我不是在原地打转，浪费时间

482
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:25,480
-You know Chandler. -No,I don't know Chandler.
你也了解钱德  我已经不了解钱德了

484
00:29:25,690 --> 00:29:29,920
Not anymore. It's like something's changed.
仿佛有什么事变了

485
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:33,660
-Maybe you changed. -I didn't change.
也许是你变了？ 我才没变

487
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:35,830
Maybe that's the problem.
也许问题就在这里

488
00:29:37,540 --> 00:29:40,400
-What? -Chandler is a complex fellow.
什么？ 钱德很复杂

490
00:29:40,610 --> 00:29:43,300
One who is unlikely to take a wife.
不太可能成亲

491
00:29:45,450 --> 00:29:47,880
Is that some kind of boat talk?
这是跑船人的用语吗？

492
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:52,050
I haven't totally decided how to talk on my boat yet.
我还没想好在船上的说话风格

493
00:29:54,290 --> 00:29:57,450
Does he think I'll wait around for nothing?
他以为我会空等下去吗？

494
00:29:57,660 --> 00:30:00,820
Face it. Chandler is against marriage.
面对现实吧，钱德反对婚姻 

495
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:02,890
And always will be.
他是不会变了

496
00:30:04,130 --> 00:30:07,030
There's some people who do wanna marry me.
有些人可是真心想娶我

497
00:30:07,230 --> 00:30:09,530
-There are? -Yeah. Richard.
有吗？ 有，理查

499
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:12,900
Richard said he wants to marry you?
理查说他想娶你？

500
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:17,410
-And Chandler says he hates marriage? -That's right.
钱德说他痛恨婚姻？ 没错

501
00:30:17,610 --> 00:30:19,480
Chandler loves marriage!
钱德热爱婚姻

502
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:23,880
You just said he hates marriage!
你刚才说他痛恨婚姻

503
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:27,640
"He's a complex fellow who's unlikely to take a wife"!
说他很复杂，不太可能娶妻

504
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:30,980
"He's against marriage and always will be"!
说他会永远反对婚姻

505
00:30:31,190 --> 00:30:33,630
You got that from what I said?
你的解读是这样？

506
00:30:39,430 --> 00:30:42,960
After the Cretaceous Period, the dinosaurs were gone.
白垩纪结束，恐龙也从此绝迹

507
00:30:43,170 --> 00:30:46,000
What happened,you guys?
你们究竟怎么了？

508
00:30:53,080 --> 00:30:55,510
-Rach. -Hey,you.
瑞秋 帅哥

509
00:30:57,150 --> 00:30:58,780
-Come on in. -Thank you.
请进 谢谢

510
00:30:59,250 --> 00:31:02,310
I'm so sorry to hear about you and Elizabeth.
很遗撼你跟伊丽莎白分手了

511
00:31:02,520 --> 00:31:06,620
Thanks. I really thought we'd be able to make it work.
谢谢，我以为我们能克服万难 

512
00:31:06,830 --> 00:31:08,990
I guess it wasn't meant to be.
这大概是命中注定的

513
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:13,600
Yeah. Love. It's a tricky business,isn't it?
是啊，爱情…爱情真是微妙

514
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:18,660
-I guess so. -So,what do you say we make a pact?
是啊  我们要不要来做个约定

516
00:31:18,870 --> 00:31:22,330
If you and I are both single by 40, we get married.
要是我们到了40都还没结婚 我们就结婚

517
00:31:22,540 --> 00:31:25,740
I mean,we know each other, we like each other...
我们互相认识，互相喜欢

518
00:31:25,950 --> 00:31:29,970
we've already slept together, so there'll be no surprises.
我们已经上过床，不会有意外

519
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,910
No, like, "What's that?"
不会觉得“搞什么？”

520
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:39,490
-Oh,you want me to be your backup. -Exactly.
你想找我当备胎？ 没错

521
00:31:39,690 --> 00:31:41,820
Yeah. I already have one.
我已经有备胎了

522
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,650
-What? Who? -Phoebe.
是谁？ 菲比

523
00:31:44,860 --> 00:31:46,390
Phoebe?
菲比？

524
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:49,770
But she just said Joey is her backup.
但是她说乔伊是她的备胎

525
00:31:49,970 --> 00:31:52,130
Oh,I don't think so.
才不是呢

526
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:56,830
We just spoke. She said that she and Joey made a deal.
罗斯，我刚跟她聊过 她说她和乔伊约好了

527
00:31:57,040 --> 00:32:01,480
That's impossible. We have had a deal for years. We shook on it.
不可能的，我们早就约好了 还握手为定

528
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:05,880
Although, believe me, she wanted to do a lot more than that.
只不过她觉得握手还不够…

529
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:10,920
Gunther, it's Joey. Is Chandler there?
阿甘，我是乔伊，钱德在吗？

530
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:15,530
Listen. What kind of muffins do they serve at sea?
我问你，跑船都吃哪一种松糕

531
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:20,330
Where the hell have you been?!
你上哪去了？

532
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:24,160
I was making a coconut phone with the Professor.
我在跟教授做椰子电话

533
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:28,500
Richard told Monica he wants to marry her.
理查跟摩妮卡说他想娶她

534
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:32,300
-What? -I've been trying to find you.
什么？ 就是啊，我一直想去找你 叫你别玩了

536
00:32:32,510 --> 00:32:37,070
And I would have if these damn boat shoes wouldn't keep flying off!
可是这双鞋子跑一跑就掉

537
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,770
-Oh,my God! -I know! They suck!
我的天哪  就是啊，烂死了

538
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:43,250
He's not supposed to ask her to marry him! I am!
他不该向我的女朋友求婚 该求婚的人是我

539
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:44,750
-I know! -What..?
我知道 那…

540
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:49,050
You know what I'll do? I'll go over there and kick his ass!
你知道吗？我要去找他教训他

541
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,630
Will you help me?
你愿意帮忙吗？

542
00:32:52,370 --> 00:32:57,530
Look, I don't think us getting our asses kicked is a solution, okay?
钱德，被他海扁一顿不是办法

543
00:32:57,740 --> 00:33:01,170
-Look,just go and find Monica. -You're right.
赶快去找摩妮卡吧  你说得对

544
00:33:01,370 --> 00:33:03,740
Okay. I'm gonna get the ring...
好 我去拿戒指...

546
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:07,040
I'm gonna go find her and I'm gonna propose!
我要找到她，直接向她求婚

547
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:10,040
Dude! Dude! Dude!
老兄 怎样？

549
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:13,580
That coconut phone might be good for the boat.
你的椰子电话 也许很适合摆在船上

550
00:33:28,170 --> 00:33:29,430
Hi.

551
00:33:31,970 --> 00:33:33,270
Hi.

552
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,810
I don't know why I'm here.
我不知道我来干什么

553
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,040
I didn't ask.
我又没问

554
00:33:42,450 --> 00:33:45,710
-You wanna come in? -I don't know.
你要进来吗？ 我不知道

555
00:33:46,490 --> 00:33:48,220
Oh,okay.
好吧

556
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:52,520
I'll just leave the door open and sit on the couch.
那我把门开着，回去坐下

557
00:33:54,490 --> 00:33:57,860
-Chandler is such an idiot! -Drink?
钱德真是个白痴  喝酒？

559
00:33:59,130 --> 00:34:02,160
-Scotch on the.. -Rocks with a twist?
好，我要威士忌加… 冰块和莱姆片？

560
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:03,890
I remember.
我记得

561
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:08,870
You still smoking cigars?
还在抽雪茄？

562
00:34:09,740 --> 00:34:12,210
No, no. That's art.
没有，那是艺术

563
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:16,940
If it bothers you, I can put my art out.
如果你不喜欢 我可以把艺术熄掉

564
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:19,650
No,that's okay.
没关系

565
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:25,650
So, Monica, let me ask you a question.
摩妮卡，我问你一件事

566
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:28,790
Since we broke up, do you ever...
我们分手后，你有...

567
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:30,620
think about me?
想过我吗？

568
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:34,460
Actually,I thought about you a few months ago.
我2个月前还想到你

569
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:36,600
-Really? -But it's because...
是吗？ 不过是因为...

570
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:40,530
I had an eye exam, and I don't like my new eye doctor.
我去做眼睛检查 又不喜欢我的新医生

571
00:34:41,670 --> 00:34:43,300
-Who is it? -Edward Nevsky.
是谁？ 爱德华奈夫斯基

572
00:34:43,640 --> 00:34:44,940
He's no good.
他的确很差

573
00:34:47,010 --> 00:34:50,180
Do you ever think about me...
你有想过...

574
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:54,110
-in a non-eye-doctor way? -No.
非眼科医生的我吗？ 没有

576
00:34:58,420 --> 00:35:02,660
Because getting over you was the hardest thing I've ever done.
但忘记你是我这辈子最难的事

577
00:35:03,130 --> 00:35:06,000
I never let myself think about you.
我不让自己想到你

578
00:35:06,530 --> 00:35:08,090
Wow.

579
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:16,010
Phoebe, you picked Joey and Ross?
菲比 你找了乔伊和罗斯？

581
00:35:16,210 --> 00:35:20,040
-You can't have two backups! -Of course I can.
你不能有两个备胎 当然可以

583
00:35:20,250 --> 00:35:23,110
It's good sense to back up your backup.
眼光独到才会替备胎找备胎

584
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:25,940
-Look, I've already lost Chandler. -What?
我已经折损钱德了 什么？

585
00:35:26,850 --> 00:35:29,620
Hey, Phoebe! We're both your backup?
菲比，我们都是你的备胎？

586
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:32,520
How could you do this to me?
菲比，你怎么可以这样？

587
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:37,430
Why are you complaining? You were both aware of the situation.
我不知道你们在抱怨什么 你们都知道这个状况

588
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:39,530
-I was not! -No,we weren't!
我们不知道 我不知道

589
00:35:39,730 --> 00:35:43,360
This kind of backtalk won't fly when we're married.
婚后你们可不能这样顶嘴

590
